					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The core idea here is familiar—shades of <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4205">SCP-4205</a> and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Bells_of_Saint_John">Dr. Who</a>—but the approach of setting a <a href="https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DwindlingParty">Dwindling Party scenario</a> in a computer was plenty novel and entertaining enough to set it apart imo.</p> 
				 	]]>
